      <title>高盛策略师表示股市不太可能陷入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/goldman-strategists-say-stocks-unlikely-to-sink-into-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团策略师表示，由于美联储预计将降息，经济衰退的风险仍然很低，美国股市不太可能下跌 20% 或更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/goldman-strategists-say-stocks-unlikely-to-sink-into-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:17:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《福布斯》报道，俄罗斯将斥资 6.46 亿美元封锁 VPN</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/russia-to-spend-646-million-to-block-vpns-forbes-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《福布斯》俄罗斯版周二报道，俄罗斯通信监管机构 Roskomnadzor 计划在未来五年内斥资 590 亿卢布（6.44 亿美元）升级其互联网流量过滤能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/russia-to-spend-646-million-to-block-vpns-forbes-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行持有的中国债券交易量激增，显示出干预的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pboc-owned-china-bonds-see-trading-surge-in-sign-of-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员发现，一些主要由央行持有的中国特别国债的交易量激增，这一迹象表明，当局可能已更加积极地出售其持有的债券，以给火热的股市上涨降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/pboc-owned-china-bonds-see-trading-surge-in-sign-of-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
